\v 9-10 \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* solemnly promised that he would not allow Saul and his descendants to continue to rule. He promised that he would cause David to rule over all the tribes of Israel and Judah, from Dan \add city\add* far in the north to Beersheba \add city\add* far in the south. So I hope/desire that God will punish me severely [HYP] if I do not enable that to happen!”
