\v 13 \w When|strong="H7725"\w* \w David|strong="H1732"\w* \w returned|strong="H7725"\w* \add after defeating the armies of Syria\add*, \w he|strong="H6213"\w* \w became|strong="H7725"\w* \w more|strong="H6213"\w* \w famous|strong="H8034"\w* because \w his|strong="H1732"\w* army \w killed|strong="H5221"\w* 18,000 soldiers \w from|strong="H7725"\w* \w the|strong="H5221"\w* Edom people-group \w in|strong="H6213"\w* \w the|strong="H5221"\w* \w Salt|strong="H4417"\w* \w Valley|strong="H1516"\w* \add near the Dead Sea\add*.
