\c 9
\s1 David was kind to Mephibosheth
\p 
\v 1 \w One|strong="H3588"\w* day \w David|strong="H1732"\w* asked, “\w Is|strong="H3426"\w* \w there|strong="H3426"\w* \w anyone|strong="H3588"\w* \w who|strong="H3588"\w* \w is|strong="H3426"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* descendant \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w Saul|strong="H7586"\w* \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w whom|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w can|strong="H6213"\w* \w be|strong="H3426"\w* kind?” \w He|strong="H3588"\w* asked \w this|strong="H6213"\w* \w because|strong="H3588"\w* \w he|strong="H3588"\w* wanted \w to|strong="H6213"\w* honor \w Jonathan|strong="H3083"\w*.
