\v 5 \w But|strong="H1571"\w* Absalom \w said|strong="H7121"\w*, “\w Summon|strong="H7121"\w* \w Hushai|strong="H2365"\w* \w also|strong="H1571"\w*, \w and|strong="H8085"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H1571"\w* \w hear|strong="H8085"\w* \w what|strong="H4100"\w* \w he|strong="H1931"\w* suggests.”
\v 6 \w So|strong="H6213"\w* \w when|strong="H1696"\w* \w Hushai|strong="H2365"\w* arrived, Absalom \w told|strong="H1696"\w* \w him|strong="H6213"\w* \w what|strong="H1697"\w* Ahithophel \w had|strong="H2365"\w* suggested. \w Then|strong="H1696"\w* \w he|strong="H6213"\w* \w asked|strong="H1696"\w* \w Hushai|strong="H2365"\w*, “\w What|strong="H1697"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w* \w you|strong="H6213"\w* think \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w should|strong="H6213"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w*? If \w you|strong="H6213"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w* \w not|strong="H6213"\w* think \w that|strong="H1697"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w should|strong="H6213"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w* \w what|strong="H1697"\w* Ahithophel suggests, \w tell|strong="H1696"\w* \w us|strong="H6213"\w* \add what you think that we should do\add*.”
