\p 
\v 14 Absalom \w and|strong="H3478"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w other|strong="H3605"\w* Israeli \w men|strong="H7451"\w* \add who were with him\add* said, “\w What|strong="H2896"\w* \w Hushai|strong="H2365"\w* suggests \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w better|strong="H2896"\w* \w than|strong="H2896"\w* \w what|strong="H2896"\w* Ahithophel suggested.” \w The|strong="H3605"\w* \w reason|strong="H5668"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* happened \w was|strong="H3068"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w had|strong="H3068"\w* determined \w that|strong="H3605"\w* if \w they|strong="H3068"\w* \w would|strong="H3068"\w* accept \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w good|strong="H2896"\w* \w advice|strong="H6098"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* Ahithophel \w had|strong="H3068"\w* \w given|strong="H6680"\w* \w them|strong="H6680"\w*, \add they would have been able to defeat/kill David\add*. \w But|strong="H3605"\w* \add as a result of their doing what Hushai suggested\add*, \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w would|strong="H3068"\w* cause \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w disaster|strong="H7451"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* happen \w to|strong="H3478"\w* Absalom.
\s1 Hushai arranged for a report to be sent to David
\p 
